{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.commandConfigElab\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">commandConfigElab</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`declare_command_config_elab_legacy elabName TypeName` declares a function `elabName : Syntax → CommandElabM TypeName`\nthat elaborates a command configuration.\nThe configuration can be from `Lean.Parser.Tactic.optConfig` or `Lean.Parser.Tactic.config`,\nand these can also be wrapped in null nodes (for example, from `(config)?`).\n\nThe elaborator has error recovery enabled.\n\nThis command has been deprecated since 2026-05-14. Use `declare_command_config_elab` instead.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.commandConfigElab","kind":"def","line":212,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.commandConfigElab","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.lean#L212-L213"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.configElab\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">configElab</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`declare_config_elab_legacy elabName TypeName` declares a function `elabName : Syntax → TacticM TypeName`\nthat elaborates a tactic configuration.\nThe tactic configuration can be from `Lean.Parser.Tactic.optConfig` or `Lean.Parser.Tactic.config`,\nand these can also be wrapped in null nodes (for example, from `(config)?`).\n\nThe elaborator responds to the current recovery state.\n\nFor defining elaborators for commands, use `declare_command_config_elab`.\n\nThis command has been deprecated since 2026-05-14. Use `declare_config_elab` instead.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.configElab","kind":"def","line":195,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.configElab","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.lean#L195-L196"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.elabConfig\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabConfig</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">recover</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">structName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">items</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.ConfigItemView\">ConfigItemView</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Term/TermElabM.html#Lean.Elab.Term.TermElabM\">TermElabM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Elaborates a tactic configuration. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.elabConfig","kind":"def","line":85,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.elabConfig","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.lean#L85-L137"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.mkConfigItemViews\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkConfigItemViews</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntaxArray\">TSyntaxArray</a> <span class=\"fn\">`Lean.Parser.Tactic.configItem</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.ConfigItemView\">ConfigItemView</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Interprets the `config` as an array of option/value pairs. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.mkConfigItemViews","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.mkConfigItemViews","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.lean#L44-L52"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.ConfigItemView.bool\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">ConfigItemView</span>.<span class=\"name\">bool</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Config.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.ConfigItemView\">ConfigItemView</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Whether thi